<li>Technical Service Maps BCV/SSL/Tube Lines etc <a href="http://www.cryptart.com/tube" class="external text" title="http://www.cryptart.com/tube" rel="nofollow">Technical Maps</a></li>
<li>Tube Professionals’ RUmour NEtwork <a href="http://www.trainweb.org/tubeprune/index.htm" class="external text" title="http://www.trainweb.org/tubeprune/index.htm" rel="nofollow">The Tubeprune</a></li>
<li>Stephen Knight’s <a href="http://www.chesapeake.net/~cambronj/lu/track_schematics/index.htm" class="external text" title="http://www.chesapeake.net/~cambronj/lu/track_schematics/index.htm" rel="nofollow">London Underground Track Maps</a> (Site broken. <a href="http://web.archive.org/web/20060310214839/www.chesapeake.net/~cambronj/lu/track_schematics/index.htm" class="external text" title="http://web.archive.org/web/20060310214839/www.chesapeake.net/~cambronj/lu/track_schematics/index.htm" rel="nofollow">Archived version</a> on the <a href="/wiki/Internet_Archive" title="Internet Archive">Internet Archive</a>.)</li>
</ul>
